videos.description: Louisville's Jordan Nwora goes through the defense and is able to finish the one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Nwora goes right down the lane for the jam

videos.description: Clemson big man Elijah Thomas tries to shoot from the floor, misses, then it gets tapped out to Marcquise Reed for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Clemson player tries to shoot from floor
